<subSubSection pageId="239" pageNumber="844" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="239.[165,1376,1554,2490]" pageId="239" pageNumber="844">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[170,523,2265,2294]" pageId="239" pageNumber="844">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List (as R. ar-Jakienis). The Vogelkop Mountain Rat is known from very few specimens in the Arfak National Reserve. More research is needed to fully understand its natural history and conservation threats.
</paragraph>
